{"tid":1276424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［死黑警］一件隔一個街口嘅事","createTime":"2019-07-02T03:04:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T03:51:29.000Z","uid":49524,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d1c6ed618c0cdaf7398bfcc599abe2d3dccdc33b","tid":1276424,"uid":49524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:04:48.000Z","msg":"係夜晚10:00左右<br />\n遊行人士都到左尾聲<br />\n交通犬都出黎準備開返路<br />\n<br />\n咁有兩個外國遊客唔知頭唔知路<br />\n坐住的士去到交通犬封路嘅位置<br />\n被手勢告知左前面去唔到 要掉頭<br />\n<br />\n咁兩個外國遊客就打算落車再行去佢地要去嘅地方<br />\n但係俾錢找錢呢樣嘢處理得有啲耐(一兩分鐘左右）<br />\n<br />\n隻交通犬突然大叫<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">搞撚掂未呀！<br />\n係咪玩嘢呀！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n想講嘅係啲狗對住三個同71遊行示威活動完全冇關係嘅人都惡言相向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲狗究竟仲可唔可以係一個冷靜嘅情況下執法<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母死黑警</span></span>"},{"pid":"e54745027b80899f0fe4a8540d12eb8d2d394766","tid":1276424,"uid":196077,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:10:57.000Z","msg":"汪汪汪"},{"pid":"96d76e2d298dfbc7ac7ca038d8c0eb700777be52","tid":1276424,"uid":49524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:11:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9ea8a62a3e825142a769c105f24a66edfd37eee","tid":1276424,"uid":259166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:14:09.000Z","msg":"贊，的士司機好醒目。<br />\n<br />\n黑警食屎啦你地！"},{"pid":"6fc7125bee97075326f4862f5b36220e0e6b6ba4","tid":1276424,"uid":45402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:21:32.000Z","msg":"班狗唔識講英文好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b2465f7d07ebb45ffae5d8930c40dcde44339df","tid":1276424,"uid":51594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:32:11.000Z","msg":"發夢尋晩臨清場前經狗總走 行行下有一隊齊裝狗喺旅遊車落嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同行幾條友全部比狗撞埋牆一野扯甩口罩同比人問候 有人比狗